Author: bunnyloverbunny
Text: this sounds fucked up and hard. i'm so sorry. i hope you can both heal.

Author: hunnyangel
Text: Relationships with someone who also has an ED can be really difficult. My girlfriend and I (I’m also female) were in a restrictive state in our EDs at the same time during sophomore year and it was so hard bc we’d both be hypocritical by telling the the other one to eat. I’m really sorry you have to go through this, because I know how unfair and helpless it feels. I hope things get better for you soon. No one likes to be trapped in a corner like that :-(
